Uganda Securities Exchange Increases Trading Days to 5 From 3 From Today

-- B y   F r e d   O j a m b o
-- 
2011-03-07T07:09:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-07/uganda-securities-exchange-increases-trading-days-to-5-from-3-from-today.html
The Uganda Securities Exchange
increased the number of trading days to five from three from
today, the Kampala-based bourse said in a statement on its
wesite.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Ojambo in Kampala at 
